&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Visakhapatnam.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/in_news.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;In News&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The fifth edition of the Indo-Indonesian Joint Bilateral Maritime Exercise, &amp;lsquo;Samudra Shakti &amp;ndash; 2025&amp;rsquo;, is being hosted at Visakhapatnam by the Indian Navy.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Exercise &amp;lsquo;Samudra Shakti&amp;rsquo; aims at enhancing interoperability and strengthening mutual understanding between the Indian and Indonesian navies.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The exercise was first conducted in 2018 and is a key bilateral engagement between the two countries.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The exercise consists of two phases: Harbour Phase and Sea Phase.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Sea Phase includes various operational coordination exercises such as Helicopter Operations, Air Defence Exercises, and Weapon Firing Drills.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Harbour Phase&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Focuses on building camaraderie and enhancing professional understanding between the two navies.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Sea Phase&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Involves complex operational coordination with drills such as VBSS (Visit, Board, Search and Seizure), Helicopter Operations, and Air Defence Exercises.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;These activities improve the capabilities of both navies in responding to various maritime challenges.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

