&lt;p data-end=&quot;57&quot; data-start=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li data-end=&quot;284&quot; data-start=&quot;78&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Incident Details:&lt;/strong&gt; On &lt;strong&gt;22 May 2025&lt;/strong&gt;, Israeli forces reportedly fired &lt;strong&gt;warning shots&lt;/strong&gt; near a delegation of diplomats visiting the &lt;strong&gt;West Bank&lt;/strong&gt;. This act led to widespread &lt;strong&gt;international condemnation&lt;/strong&gt; as the situation in the region remains highly sensitive due to ongoing territorial disputes.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li data-end=&quot;605&quot; data-start=&quot;482&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The West Bank:&lt;/strong&gt; The &lt;strong&gt;West Bank&lt;/strong&gt; is a region located to the east of Israel and west of Jordan. It has been a disputed territory since the &lt;strong&gt;Israeli-Palestinian conflict&lt;/strong&gt;, with Palestinians seeking it as part of their future state.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li data-end=&quot;692&quot; data-start=&quot;610&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Diplomatic Delegation:&lt;/strong&gt; The delegation of diplomats was present in the area as part of an effort to assess the situation on the ground, aiming to understand the challenges faced by the Palestinian population and the complexities of the conflict. Their presence highlights the ongoing international efforts for a peaceful resolution.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li data-end=&quot;1041&quot; data-start=&quot;850&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Israel&amp;#39;s Actions:&lt;/strong&gt; The firing of warning shots by Israeli forces was seen as a provocative move, drawing criticism from various countries and international organizations. It underscores the tense and fragile situation in the &lt;strong&gt;West Bank&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li data-end=&quot;1162&quot; data-start=&quot;1046&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;International Response:&lt;/strong&gt; This incident led to widespread condemnation, with calls for restraint and peaceful dialogue between Israel and Palestine. The international community has consistently urged both parties to avoid actions that could escalate tensions.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li data-end=&quot;1560&quot; data-start=&quot;1323&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Historical Context:&lt;/strong&gt; The &lt;strong&gt;West Bank&lt;/strong&gt; has been a flashpoint in the &lt;strong&gt;Israeli-Palestinian conflict&lt;/strong&gt; since Israel&amp;#39;s occupation of the territory following the &lt;strong&gt;Six-Day War&lt;/strong&gt; in 1967. The area is central to discussions about the establishment of a two-state solution.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li data-end=&quot;1654&quot; data-start=&quot;1565&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Hence, the correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;West Bank&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;West Bank:&lt;/strong&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li data-end=&quot;2410&quot; data-start=&quot;2195&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt; The &lt;strong&gt;West Bank&lt;/strong&gt; is situated between Israel and Jordan, encompassing cities such as &lt;strong&gt;Ramallah, Nablus&lt;/strong&gt;, and &lt;strong&gt;Hebron&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-end=&quot;2684&quot; data-start=&quot;2415&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Population:&lt;/strong&gt; It is home to approximately &lt;strong&gt;2.9 million Palestinians&lt;/strong&gt;, along with Israeli settlers living in settlements deemed illegal under international law.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-end=&quot;2860&quot; data-start=&quot;2735&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Historical Significance:&lt;/strong&gt; The region has immense religious and historical importance for Jews, Christians, and Muslims, contributing to the complexity of the conflict.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-end=&quot;3071&quot; data-start=&quot;2865&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Territorial Dispute:&lt;/strong&gt; The &lt;strong&gt;West Bank&lt;/strong&gt; remains central to the Israeli-Palestinian conflict, with Palestinians demanding it as part of their future state and Israel maintaining control over certain areas.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;International Condemnation:&lt;/strong&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li data-end=&quot;3250&quot; data-start=&quot;3076&quot;&gt;Incidents such as firing warning shots near diplomats often result in strong international criticism, with countries and organizations emphasizing the need for restraint.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-end=&quot;3402&quot; data-start=&quot;3301&quot;&gt;The incident underscores the importance of international diplomatic efforts in resolving the conflict and achieving peace in the region.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Israeli-Palestinian Conflict:&lt;/strong&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li data-end=&quot;3580&quot; data-start=&quot;3407&quot;&gt;The conflict dates back to the early 20th century, with disputes over land, sovereignty, and national identity.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-end=&quot;3729&quot; data-start=&quot;3585&quot;&gt;Efforts to achieve a two-state solution remain ongoing but have faced numerous challenges, including settlements and security concerns.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/important-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Important Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Israeli Settlements:&lt;/strong&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li data-end=&quot;4636&quot; data-start=&quot;4411&quot;&gt;Israeli settlements in the &lt;strong&gt;West Bank&lt;/strong&gt; are considered illegal under &lt;strong&gt;international law&lt;/strong&gt;, specifically the &lt;strong&gt;Fourth Geneva Convention&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-end=&quot;4761&quot; data-start=&quot;4641&quot;&gt;Despite this, Israel has continued settlement expansion, leading to tensions and criticism from the global community.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Diplomatic Efforts:&lt;/strong&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li data-end=&quot;5043&quot; data-start=&quot;4817&quot;&gt;Numerous diplomatic efforts, including those led by the &lt;strong&gt;United Nations&lt;/strong&gt;, the &lt;strong&gt;United States&lt;/strong&gt;, and other international bodies, aim to mediate peace between Israel and Palestine.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-end=&quot;5259&quot; data-start=&quot;5048&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Oslo Accords:&lt;/strong&gt; Signed in the 1990s, these agreements aimed to establish a framework for peace but have faced implementation challenges.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
